# Cursor Prompt Structure

Every prompt must follow:

```
SCOPE — STRICT: Modify ONLY [file(s)].
Do not modify any other file.

DIAGNOSTIC FIRST:
Read the file and report its current state before making any changes.

[Changes in detail, exact copy if content-related]

DO NOT MODIFY:
- [list every other file explicitly]

CRITICAL: All copy must be in English — exact text provided. Do not change wording.

npm run build must pass.
Report what you changed.
```

## Slicing

Break large features into 2–3 prompts: **A.1** static layout + copy → **A.2** styling + effects → **B** animations + interactions.

## Content guard

Always provide exact copy in the prompt. Never let the agent generate or paraphrase marketing/content text.
